Reality TV star, Dorathy Bachor has lambasted people who ask for others account details yet fail to send them money. The former BBNaija “Lockdown” housemate lamented the anguish those who give their account details with hopes of receiving alert have to endure which is further heightened when they get disappointed.   Garba Shehu follows Tinubu media support group on twitter     My life has become sweet, says hawker who gave inmates money     I was depressed but lived in denial – Toyin Abraham   According to the entrepreneur via an insta story, those who are guilty of this act have a special place reserved for them in hell. The plus-size model wrote: “No greater pain than that person that asked for your account details and didn’t send anything. You didn’t beg them o. You have a special place in hell.”